text: Fiona Wentges (born 3 February 1958) is an Irish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Irish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
